headlines.description: — The 76ers fans came to boo Ben Simmons. They left booing their own team.
headlines.shortLinkText: Durant, Nets rout 76ers in Simmons' return to Philadelphia

events.name: Golden State Warriors at Denver Nuggets

headlines.description: — Stephen Curry scored 24 of his 34 points in the second half, and the Golden State Warriors closed the game with a 13-0 run to beat the Denver Nuggets 113-102 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Curry scores 34 points, Warriors beat Nuggets 113-102
